#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.110"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.110:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.110:0.2"
msgid "11. Tikavagga"
msgstr "11. Triads"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.110:0.3"
msgid "110. Saññāsutta"
msgstr "110. Perceptions"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.447"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.110:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, dhammā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three things."

msgctxt "an6.110:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an6.110:1.3"
msgid "Kāmasaññā, byāpādasaññā, vihiṃsāsaññā."
msgstr "Sensual, malicious, and cruel perceptions."

msgctxt "an6.110:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhammā."
msgstr "These are the three things."

msgctxt "an6.110:1.5"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr "To give up these three things you should develop three things."

msgctxt "an6.110:1.6"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an6.110:1.7"
msgid ""
"Kāmasaññāya pahānāya nekkhammasaññā bhāvetabbā, byāpādasaññāya pahānāya "
"abyāpādasaññā bhāvetabbā, vihiṃsāsaññāya pahānāya avihiṃsāsaññā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr ""
"You should develop perceptions of renunciation to give up sensual "
"perceptions, perceptions of love to give up malicious perceptions, and "
"perceptions of kindness to give up cruel perceptions."

msgctxt "an6.110:1.8"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya ime tayo dhammā "
"bhāvetabbā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the three things you should develop to give up those three things.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.110:1.9"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
